org.metastatic.rsync

Class Generator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.metastatic.rsync.Generator

  • public class Generator
extends java.lang.Object
    A checksum generator. This class can take a byte array or an input stream, and will generate a list of ChecksumPair objects for that data.
